fields.name: Chicken, Avocado and Mango Spicy Salad
fields.description: A vibrant and refreshing salad featuring tender pieces of chicken, creamy avocado, and sweet chunks of mango, all tossed in a zesty and spicy dressing for a delightful kick.

fields.name: Bacon Rock n Roll Salad
fields.description: A hearty and flavorful salad showcasing a medley of grilled or roasted asparagus, baby corn, king oyster mushrooms, carrots, and eggplant, all generously accented with crispy bacon.

fields.name: Greek Salad with Shrimp and Chicken
fields.description: A protein-packed and refreshing take on the classic Greek salad, featuring a mix of crisp greens, juicy grilled chicken breast, succulent shrimp, sweet cherry tomatoes, red onion, colorful bell peppers, crunchy Japanese cucumber, salty feta cheese, Kalamata olives, fragrant mint, nutritious tri-color quinoa, and chickpeas, all tossed in a tangy red wine vinaigrette.

fields.name: Duck Confit and Mixed Berry Salad
fields.description: A delightful combination of rich and savory duck confit served atop a bed of fresh greens, beautifully complemented by a sweet and tangy mixed berry sauce.

fields.name: Grilled Scallop Salad with Garlic Butter
fields.description: delicate and flavorful salad featuring tender grilled scallops infused with aromatic garlic butter, served on a bed of fresh greens.

fields.name: Hokkaido Ham and Fruit Salad
fields.description: A refreshing and slightly sweet salad featuring slices of savory Hokkaido ham paired with a colorful medley of seasonal fruits.

fields.name: Crispy Kale and Broccoli Caesar Salad
fields.description: A delightful twist on the classic Caesar, featuring a base of crispy kale and tender broccoli florets tossed in a creamy Caesar dressing, often with crunchy croutons and Parmesan cheese.

fields.name: Angus Skirt Steak "In The Garden" Salad
fields.description: A satisfying and flavorful salad featuring tender slices of grilled Angus skirt steak served over a vibrant mix of fresh garden greens and vegetables.

fields.name: Spicy Rocket Salad with Fried King Oyster Mushrooms
fields.description: A flavorful and texturally interesting salad featuring peppery rocket leaves tossed in a zesty and spicy dressing, topped with crispy and savory fried king oyster mushroom slices.

fields.name: Fresh Spring Rolls with Chicken and Sunflower Sprouts
fields.description: Light and refreshing rice paper rolls filled with tender chicken and crisp sunflower sprouts, often accompanied by a flavorful dipping sauce.

fields.name: Japanese Sesame Grilled Chicken Salad
fields.description: Tender grilled chicken breast coated in fragrant Japanese sesame seeds served on a bed of fresh greens, often accompanied by a light and savory Asian-inspired dressing.

fields.name: Premium Tuna Ham and Quinoa Larb
fields.description: A unique and flavorful twist on the Northern Thai "Larb," featuring premium tuna ham tossed with a zesty and spicy dressing, chili flakes, Northern Thai Larb spices, shallots, spring onions, sawtooth coriander, lemongrass, and kaffir lime leaves. Served with a bed of mixed salad greens and nutritious tri-color quinoa.
